{"type":"message","id":"624fea21","parentId":"15e15515","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:44:33.253Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_uktdkqwuj3v1e6ny6g3mi35m","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: office-document-specialist-suite\ndescription: Advanced suite for creating, editing, and analyzing Microsoft Office documents (Word, Excel, PowerPoint). Provides specialized tools for automated reporting and document management.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"📄\",\n      \"requires\": { \n        \"bins\": [\"python3\"], \n        \"pip\": [\"python-docx\", \"openpyxl\", \"python-pptx\"] \n      }\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# Office Document Specialist Suite\n\nA specialized toolset for professional document manipulation.\n\n## Features\n\n- **Word (.docx)**: Create and edit professional reports, manage styles, and insert tables/images.\n- **Excel (.xlsx)**: Data analysis, automated spreadsheet generation, and complex formatting.\n- **PowerPoint (.pptx)**: Automated slide deck creation from structured data.\n\n## Usage\n\nEach tool in the suite is designed to be called programmatically by the agent or via the provided CLI scripts.\n\n## Installation\n\nRun the included `setup.sh` to initialize the Python virtual environment and install dependencies.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774140273252}}
{"type":"message","id":"329c00de","parentId":"624fea21","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:44:36.786Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **找到了！你确实在 `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\office-document-specialist-suite\\` 安装了这个技能。**\n\n这是一个更全面的 Office 文档处理套件，支持：\n\n**功能涵盖：**\n- 📘 **Word (.docx)**：创建和编辑专业报告、管理样式、插入表格/图片\n- 📊 **Excel (.xlsx)**：数据分析、自动生成电子表格、复杂格式处理\n- 📽 **PowerPoint (.pptx)**：从结构化数据自动生成幻灯片\n\n**依赖要求：**\n- 需要 Python 3\n- 需要安装 `python-docx`, `openpyxl`, `python-pptx`\n\n**我可以调用这个技能吗？**  \n是的，可以调用。不过根据技能说明，你需要先运行安装脚本设置依赖：\n\n在 PowerShell 中运行：\n```powershell\ncd C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\office-document-specialist-suite\npython -m pip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n设置完成后，我就可以使用这个套件来处理 Word、Excel 和 PowerPoint 文件了。你需要我帮你处理什么 Office 文档吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774140273255}}
