{"type":"message","id":"f1cfd811","parentId":"fbee22a3","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:53:00.139Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_wewm84x52dk0trw5ay58g4ts","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: office-document-specialist-suite\ndescription: Advanced suite for creating, editing, and analyzing Microsoft Office documents (Word, Excel, PowerPoint). Provides specialized tools for automated reporting and document management.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"📄\",\n      \"requires\": { \n        \"bins\": [\"python3\"], \n        \"pip\": [\"python-docx\", \"openpyxl\", \"python-pptx\"] \n      }\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# Office Document Specialist Suite\n\nA specialized toolset for professional document manipulation.\n\n## Features\n\n- **Word (.docx)**: Create and edit professional reports, manage styles, and insert tables/images.\n- **Excel (.xlsx)**: Data analysis, automated spreadsheet generation, and complex formatting.\n- **PowerPoint (.pptx)**: Automated slide deck creation from structured data.\n\n## Usage\n\nEach tool in the suite is designed to be called programmatically by the agent or via the provided CLI scripts.\n\n## Installation\n\nRun the included `setup.sh` to initialize the Python virtual environment and install dependencies.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774140780137}}
{"type":"message","id":"36eb1f8c","parentId":"f1cfd811","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:53:06.376Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **找到了！技能已经正确安装，我可以访问了。**\n\n安装位置：`C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\skills\\office-document-specialist-suite\\`\n\n**技能信息：**\n- 名称：Office Document Specialist Suite\n- 功能：高级 Microsoft Office 文档处理套件\n- 支持格式：\n  - 📘 Word (.docx) — 创建编辑专业报告、管理样式、插入表格/图片\n  - 📊 Excel (.xlsx) — 数据分析、自动生成电子表格、复杂格式处理\n  - 📽 PowerPoint (.pptx) — 从结构化数据自动生成幻灯片\n\n**依赖检查：**\n需要确认 Python 依赖是否已安装。你运行过 `setup.sh` 或安装了 `python-docx`, `openpyxl`, `python-pptx` 了吗？\n\n如果还没安装，我们可以现在安装依赖：\n```powershell\ncd C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\skills\\office-document-specialist-suite\npip install python-docx openpyxl python-pptx\n```\n\n安装完成后我就可以使用这个技能来处理 Office 文档了。你需要我帮你处理什么文档？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774140780140}}
